headline: Charles River and Valo Health Identify a Potential Therapeutic for Lupus Using Logica®, an AI-Powered Drug Discovery Platform
summary: WILMINGTON, Mass. & CAMBRIDGE, Mass., March 25, 2025--Charles River and Valo Health announce the identification of an advanceable product candidate for treatment of lupus and other autoimmune diseases.
